{"tid":1266482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五毛/玩膠/分化/發布假消息 User 集中貼","createTime":"2019-06-29T14:24:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T14:25:42.000Z","uid":41292,"like":31,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4aced121ec214cf4249075e0a1a4d795a2293b8b","tid":1266482,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:24:24.000Z","msg":"雖然我唔想做到關sir咁撚樣<br />\n成串user名狂彈出黎<br />\n但係今次實在太過多同倡狂<br />\n所以我覺得有必要整合依啲user<br />\n令到有Ac嘅盡量唔覆佢地/block左佢地<br />\n無Ac嘅盡量唔睇佢地<br />\n<br />\n如果要加名比多啲證據佢地係真係唔係同路<br />\n有時候失敗主義都係同路 只係佢地比人同化左<br />\n需要大量起底搵返佢講嘅野 先可以肯定<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/sEXvsEqEQbcWzetn6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FsEXvsEqEQbcWzetn6&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJoytC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=976ce6ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/sEXvsEqEQbcWzetn6</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/18P8KTaRlwoIe0PkzDyYwO5gIgVGKMZBXEBTKQ76EBFE/edit#gid=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F18P8KTaRlwoIe0PkzDyYwO5gIgVGKMZBXEBTKQ76EBFE%2Fedit%23gid%3D0&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJoytC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=5f63ff3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/18P8KTaRlwoIe0PkzDyYwO5gIgVGKMZBXEBTKQ76EBFE/edit#gid=0</a>"},{"pid":"ea71a9c73453b5e8ad08b725ccff39dd8f01feed","tid":1266482,"uid":41292,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:24:42.000Z","msg":"希望大家可以幫幫手 唔該!"},{"pid":"3b4590a7ea90cc4e4099f67e35e0d77f794654db","tid":1266482,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:29:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da44eecfdfa43617aa732b35f073f5336bd2c660","tid":1266482,"uid":41292,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:33:12.000Z","msg":"幫幫手<br />\n<br />\n如果見